exports[`golden snapshots > css 1`] = `
"/*
 * Yahoda export — CSS variables
 * system: Acme UI
 * schemaVersion: 1.0.0
 * commit: draft
 */
:root {
  /* primitives */
  --fontFamily-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
  --fontFamily-sans: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;
  --fontSize-lg: 1.25rem;
  --fontSize-md: 1rem;
  --fontSize-sm: 0.875rem;
  --fontSize-xl: clamp(2rem, 1.8261rem + 0.8696vw, 2.5rem);
  --palette-blue-600: #2448B8;
  --palette-blue-700: #1E3FA0;
  --palette-red-600: #C0341D;
  --palette-slate-300: #C4C9D1;
  --palette-slate-900: #181A1D;
  --palette-white: #FFFFFF;
  /* semantic */
  --color-border: var(--palette-slate-300);
  --color-danger: var(--palette-red-600);
  --color-primary: var(--palette-blue-600);
  --color-primaryHover: var(--palette-blue-700);
  --color-surface: var(--palette-white);
  --color-text: var(--palette-slate-900);
  --color-textOnPrimary: var(--palette-white);
  --color-transparent: transparent;
  --duration-fast: 150ms;
  --easing-standard: cubic-bezier(0.2, 0, 0, 1);
  --radius-lg: 12px;
  --radius-md: 8px;
  --radius-sm: 4px;
  --shadow-md: 0px 6px 16px -4px rgba(24,26,29,0.16);
  --shadow-sm: 0px 1px 2px 0px rgba(24,26,29,0.08);
  --spacing-1: 4px;
  --spacing-2: 8px;
  --spacing-3: 12px;
  --spacing-4: 16px;
  --spacing-6: 24px;
  --typography-body-md-font-family: var(--fontFamily-sans);
  --typography-body-md-font-size: var(--fontSize-md);
  --typography-body-md-line-height: 1.5;
  --typography-body-md-font-weight: 400;
  --typography-heading-lg-font-family: var(--fontFamily-sans);
  --typography-heading-lg-font-size: var(--fontSize-xl);
  --typography-heading-lg-line-height: 1.2;
  --typography-heading-lg-font-weight: 700;
  --typography-label-sm-font-family: var(--fontFamily-sans);
  --typography-label-sm-font-size: var(--fontSize-sm);
  --typography-label-sm-line-height: 1.4;
  --typography-label-sm-font-weight: 500;
}
"
`;

exports[`golden snapshots > markdown 1`] = `
"<!--
Yahoda export — Markdown docs
system: Acme UI
schemaVersion: 1.0.0
commit: draft
/
-->
# Acme UI

Seed/example design system for Yahoda.
## Tokens

| Token | Tier | Value | Resolved | Usage |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| \`color.border\` | semantic | → palette.slate.300 | #C4C9D1 | Default border/divider color. |
| \`color.danger\` | semantic | → palette.red.600 | #C0341D | Destructive/error emphasis. |
| \`color.primary\` | semantic | → palette.blue.600 | #2448B8 | Primary actions and brand emphasis. |
| \`color.primaryHover\` | semantic | → palette.blue.700 | #1E3FA0 | Hover/active state of primary surfaces. |
| \`color.surface\` | semantic | → palette.white | #FFFFFF | Default surface/background for components. |
| \`color.text\` | semantic | → palette.slate.900 | #181A1D | Default body text color. |
| \`color.textOnPrimary\` | semantic | → palette.white | #FFFFFF | Text/icon color on primary surfaces. |
| \`color.transparent\` | semantic | transparent |  | No fill — e.g. ghost button background. |
| \`duration.fast\` | semantic | 150ms |  | Hover/press micro-interactions. |
| \`easing.standard\` | semantic | cubic-bezier(0.2, 0, 0, 1) |  | Default easing for UI transitions. |
| \`fontFamily.mono\` | primitive | 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace |  | Code, tokens, and tabular figures. |
| \`fontFamily.sans\` | primitive | Inter, system-ui, sans-serif |  | Default UI and body typeface. |
| \`fontSize.lg\` | primitive | 1.25rem |  |  |
| \`fontSize.md\` | primitive | 1rem |  |  |
| \`fontSize.sm\` | primitive | 0.875rem |  |  |
| \`fontSize.xl\` | primitive | 2rem→2.5rem (fluid) |  | Display/heading size that scales with the viewport. |
| \`palette.blue.600\` | primitive | #2448B8 |  |  |
| \`palette.blue.700\` | primitive | #1E3FA0 |  |  |
| \`palette.red.600\` | primitive | #C0341D |  |  |
| \`palette.slate.300\` | primitive | #C4C9D1 |  |  |
| \`palette.slate.900\` | primitive | #181A1D |  |  |
| \`palette.white\` | primitive | #FFFFFF |  |  |
| \`radius.lg\` | semantic | 12px |  | Cards, dialogs. |
| \`radius.md\` | semantic | 8px |  | Buttons, alerts. |
| \`radius.sm\` | semantic | 4px |  | Inputs, badges, small controls. |
| \`shadow.md\` | semantic | 1 layer(s) |  |  |
| \`shadow.sm\` | semantic | 1 layer(s) |  |  |
| \`spacing.1\` | semantic | 4px |  |  |
| \`spacing.2\` | semantic | 8px |  |  |
| \`spacing.3\` | semantic | 12px |  |  |
| \`spacing.4\` | semantic | 16px |  |  |
| \`spacing.6\` | semantic | 24px |  |  |
| \`typography.body.md\` | semantic | →fontFamily.sans →fontSize.md/1.5 400 | Inter, system-ui, sans-serif 1rem/1.5 400 | Default body copy. |
| \`typography.heading.lg\` | semantic | →fontFamily.sans →fontSize.xl/1.2 700 | Inter, system-ui, sans-serif 2rem→2.5rem/1.2 700 | Page and section headings. |
| \`typography.label.sm\` | semantic | →fontFamily.sans →fontSize.sm/1.4 500 | Inter, system-ui, sans-serif 0.875rem/1.4 500 | Form labels and button text. |
## Components
### Alert

_Communicate an important, contextual message._

**Status:** published

**Variants:** info, danger

**States:** default

**Token bindings:**

| Property | Token |
| --- | --- |
| background | \`color.surface\` |
| color | \`color.text\` |
| borderColor | \`color.border\` |
| radius | \`radius.md\` |
| padding | \`spacing.3\` |

**Do:**
- Use for contextual, in-page messages tied to a task.

**Avoid:**
- Don't use for transient notifications — use a Toast (later).

**Accessibility (contrast):**

- color.text on color.surface: 17.44:1 AA ✓

### Badge

_Label or annotate with a small status token._

**Status:** published

**Variants:** default, danger

**States:** default

**Token bindings:**

| Property | Token |
| --- | --- |
| background | \`color.primary\` |
| color | \`color.textOnPrimary\` |
| radius | \`radius.sm\` |
| paddingX | \`spacing.2\` |

**Do:**
- Use for short status labels (1-2 words).

**Avoid:**
- Don't use Badge as a button — it is not interactive.

**Accessibility (contrast):**

- color.textOnPrimary on color.primary: 7.79:1 AA ✓

### Button

_Trigger a single, clear action._

**Status:** published

**Variants:** primary, secondary, ghost

**States:** default, hover, focus, disabled, loading

**Token bindings:**

| Property | Token |
| --- | --- |
| background | \`color.primary\` |
| color | \`color.textOnPrimary\` |
| radius | \`radius.md\` |
| paddingX | \`spacing.3\` |
| paddingY | \`spacing.2\` |
| font | \`typography.label.sm\` |
| gap | \`spacing.1\` |

**Do:**
- Use for the single primary action on a screen.

**Avoid:**
- Don't use for navigation — use a Link.
- Don't place two primary Buttons side by side.

**Accessibility (contrast):**

- color.textOnPrimary on color.primary: 7.79:1 AA ✓

**Keyboard:** Enter/Space activate

### Card

_Group related content on a surface._

**Status:** published

**Variants:** default

**States:** default

**Token bindings:**

| Property | Token |
| --- | --- |
| background | \`color.surface\` |
| radius | \`radius.lg\` |
| padding | \`spacing.4\` |
| shadow | \`shadow.sm\` |

**Do:**
- Use to group related content into a scannable unit.

**Avoid:**
- Don't nest cards more than one level deep.

**Accessibility (contrast):**

- color.text on color.surface: 17.44:1 AA ✓

### Dialog

_Interrupt the flow for a focused, modal task._

**Status:** published

**Variants:** default

**States:** open, closed

**Token bindings:**

| Property | Token |
| --- | --- |
| background | \`color.surface\` |
| radius | \`radius.lg\` |
| padding | \`spacing.6\` |
| shadow | \`shadow.md\` |

**Do:**
- Use for a focused decision or task that blocks the underlying page.

**Avoid:**
- Don't stack multiple Dialogs.
- Don't use for non-blocking info.

**Accessibility (contrast):**

- color.text on color.surface: 17.44:1 AA ✓

**Keyboard:** Esc closes, Focus is trapped, Focus returns to trigger on close

### Input

_Collect a single line of text from the user._

**Status:** published

**Variants:** default, error

**States:** default, focus, disabled

**Token bindings:**

| Property | Token |
| --- | --- |
| background | \`color.surface\` |
| color | \`color.text\` |
| borderColor | \`color.border\` |
| radius | \`radius.sm\` |
| paddingX | \`spacing.3\` |
| paddingY | \`spacing.2\` |

**Do:**
- Always pair with a visible label.

**Avoid:**
- Don't use placeholder text as the only label.

**Accessibility (contrast):**

- color.text on color.surface: 17.44:1 AA ✓
- color.border on color.surface: 1.66:1 AA ✗

**Keyboard:** Tab to focus, Type to edit

## Patterns
### Auth form

_Let a returning user sign in._

**Usage:** Use on dedicated sign-in pages, centered on the screen.

**Do:**
- Use one primary Button (Sign in) and label every Input.

**Avoid:**
- Don't add more than the fields needed to authenticate.

### Empty state

_Explain why a view is empty and offer the next action._

**Usage:** Use when a list/collection has no items yet.

**Do:**
- Explain the empty state and give one clear primary action.

**Avoid:**
- Don't show an empty state that looks like an error.

### Pricing card

_Present a single plan and its call to action._

**Usage:** Use in a row of comparable plans.

**Do:**
- Highlight at most one recommended plan with the primary Button.

**Avoid:**
- Don't overload the card with more than ~5 feature lines.

### Settings section

_Group a set of related settings with a save action._

**Usage:** Use within a settings page, one section per concern.

**Do:**
- Group related fields and provide a single save action per section.

**Avoid:**
- Don't auto-save destructive changes without confirmation.

"
`;

